Loan Approval Prediction – Insights
Dataset Insights
Credit History is often the most influential factor in loan approval decisions.
Applicants with stable income and good credit history have higher approval chances.
Missing values and categorical features require preprocessing before model training.
Model Insights
Random Forest provides reliable performance for loan approval classification.
Feature importance highlights factors that influence approval decisions.
The model can predict approval status with good accuracy.
Key Factors Affecting Loan Approval
Credit History
Applicant Income
Loan Amount
Loan Amount Term
Education
Property Area
Business Insights
Automated loan screening reduces manual effort.
Faster loan processing improves customer experience.
Consistent approval decisions reduce human bias.
Banks can assess applicant risk more efficiently.
